Text: CAN FIND ANYONE SUBTITLES FOR THIS MOVIE?
Had been looking for this movie for a long time. Please keep seeding. Will seed once I am done downloading.

WARNING BEFORE DOWNLOAING! This is in Russsian with a barely audible English dubbing and there are no subtitles. I don't know if it is a joke, an intentional f u, or an honest mistake. But do NOT waste your bandwidth. I, too, have been seeking this for years. I tried ebay and bought a vhs since this is not on DVD (why I do not understand) but the vhs turned out to be unwatchable. 
C'est la vie. So close and yet so far.
